      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for safety and mechanical integrity. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior, it offers exceptional value for the discerning driver. Professionally detailed and ready for immediate delivery.",
