    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a champ, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable, great-looking vehicle without paying those 'fresh off the lot' prices. It\u2019s clean, reliable, and ready for your next road trip. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how smoothly it handles. Drop me a message if you\u2019re interested!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit exhibits linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by its high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, and the chassis has been addressed with critical subframe reinforcement and refreshed trailing arm bushings. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, ensuring optimal torque distribution through the corners. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with a driver-focused vehicle, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain dialed for peak lateral performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2019 Toyota 4Runner SR5 Premium in Midnight Black Metallic. This vehicle has served as a reliable daily driver and remains in solid overall condition. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scuff on the rear bumper from city parking. The interior is a smoke-free environment; the black SofTex seats are free of rips or stains, though the driver\u2019s side bolster shows light creasing from entry and exit. All cabin technology\u2014including the touchscreen navigation, heated front seats, and the signature power rear window\u2014is fully operational. Mechanically, the 4.0L V6 engine performs flawlessly with no leaks or warning lights. I have followed a strict maintenance schedule, most recently replacing the front brake pads and performing a full synthetic oil change. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, providing excellent grip for the seasons ahead. This is a dependable, honest SUV that has been cared for properly. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Engineered for sustained performance and presented in an impressive state of preservation, it offers a seamless blend of mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. Each aspect of the vehicle has been vetted to ensure it meets our standards for excellence, providing an exceptional driving experience for those who value quality and long-term utility.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and the occasional road trip! It drives smoothly, looks great, and has been well-loved throughout its time with me. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable ride that\u2019s ready to go from day one, this is the one for you. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection to the limited-slip rear differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS refresh. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics with crisp turn-in and predictable lateral grip. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a driver-oriented machine for those who value chassis rigidity and powertrain integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
